1.	General
To become a user (“User”) of the Website and download the Software, please visit and register with Mozilla at (http://joey.labs.mozilla.com).  After registering, you will be able to download the Software and send electronic materials (“Digital Content”) from your Firefox web browser, by means of Mozilla’s servers, to your personal mobile device (“Mobile Device”).  Mozilla may in its sole discretion change, modify, suspend, make improvements to or discontinue any aspect of the Website temporarily or permanently, at any time and without notice to you.  Under no circumstance will Mozilla be liable for any such change, modification, suspension, improvement or discontinuance.  
2.	User Registration
By registering to become a User, you represent and warrant that the information you provide to Mozilla during the registration process is accurate, and that you will promptly notify Mozilla if any of that information changes.  Mozilla may use the information that you provide during the registration process, in particular your email address:  (a) to communicate with you about the Website and Software, including without limitation any changes to this Agreement or the Mozilla Joey Project Privacy Policy or other policies; and (b) for all other purposes stated in Mozilla’s Joey Project Privacy Policy.
3.	Age
